  <brief_title>Phase 1b Study of Omega DUROS速 in Patients With Chronic Hepatitis C Who Relapsed After Prior Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase Ib Dose Escalation Study of the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Antiviral Activity of Omega DUROS速 and Ribavirin in Subjects With Chronic Hepatitis C Previously Treated With Pegylated Interferon and Ribavirin</official_title>
