  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Omega DUROS速 is an implantable drug delivery system designed to deliver omega interferon
      subcutaneously at a constant rate for 90 days.

      This study is being performed to evaluate the safety and antiviral effects of omega
      interferon delivered by the Omega DUROS速 device in combination with ribavirin in subjects
      with chronic Hepatitis C genotype 1.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
