  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic Hepatitis C with HCV genotype 1 infection

          -  Relapse following an end of treatment response after treatment with a pegylated
             interferon and ribavirin.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Presence or history of non-HCV chronic liver disease

          -  Treatment with any interferon subsequent to the relapse with pegylated
             interferon-alpha and ribavirin

          -  Decompensated liver disease
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
